## 🚨 Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

#### CyberPot Service Not Starting
```bash
# Check service status
sudo systemctl status cyberpot

# View detailed logs
sudo journalctl -u cyberpot -n 50

# Check Docker containers
docker ps -a --filter "name=cyberpot"
```

#### Network Connectivity Issues
```bash
# Check firewall status
sudo ufw status

# Test port connectivity
telnet {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }} {{ web_port | default(64297) }}

# Check network configuration
ip route show
```

#### High Resource Usage
```bash
# Check system resources
htop

# Monitor Docker usage
docker stats

# Check disk usage
df -h
```

### Emergency Procedures

#### Stop All Services
```bash
sudo systemctl stop cyberpot
sudo systemctl stop docker
```

#### View Recent Logs
```bash
# System logs
sudo journalctl -n 100

# CyberPot logs
docker compose logs --tail=100

# Security logs
sudo tail -f /var/log/auth.log
```

#### Force Restart
```bash
sudo systemctl daemon-reload
sudo systemctl restart cyberpot
```

